item.title: Need Interface Asistance
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

Highlight the extra frame, and look at the top left corner of the screen. It will give some numbers. That is the frame (I think). To replace it, simply enter this:

sendFrame246(int (the frame), int (the size), int (item ID put as 0 or -1))
